  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“<a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Frey_(son_of_Stevron)\" title=\"Aegon Frey (son of Stevron)\">Fool</a>'s blood, <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">king</a>'s blood, blood on the <a href=\"/index.php/Roslin_Frey\" title=\"Roslin Frey\">maiden</a>'s thigh, but chains for the guests and chains for the <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">bridegroom</a>, aye aye aye.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Patchface\" title=\"Patchface\">Patchface</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_10\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 10\">Chapter 10</a>, Davos II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405220024\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 93/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 303/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 524/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    4.247      1 -total\n100.00%    4.247      1 Template:Ref\n 63.18%    2.683      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:25640-0